document_data.name: Jensena
document_data.mainbody: '''Jensena''' was a strong female soldier who drank at the [[Laughing Goblin Inn]].
document_data.Description: Jensena was tall, attractive, and had powerful muscles.
document_data.Personality: Bawdy and tough, Jensena was straight forward and could tangle with any man.
document_data.Possessions: Like her friends, [[Salen]] and [[Gwen]], Jensena fought with a [[sword]], a few [[dagger]]s, a [[throwing axe]], and wore [[chain mail]].
document_data.History: On the 19th of [[Flamerule]], [[1340 DR]], Jensena challenged [[Ren o' the Blade]] to a contest of strength, but loss to Ren's sly actions. Nine days later,
